{"tid":931003,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[等到勁都長]Apple HomePod 香港官方行貨 2019年正式開售","createTime":"2018-12-06T17:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T13:39:16.000Z","uid":4262,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad44a715cf9ca7416a1620352f9717cefdd2778","tid":931003,"uid":4262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"HomePod 早前只在美、英、澳 3 國推出，香港一直遲遲未見影。 unwire 在今年二月對其進行評測，發現 HomePod Siri 並不支援廣東話，可能因為這原因延遲在港推出。 久等的朋友有好消息，Apple Store 香港官網公佈 HomePod 香港行貨將於 2019 年推出售價為 $2,799 ，AppleCare+ 售價為 $349 。<br />\n<br />\n支援語言為英文、簡體中文、繁體中文、繁體中文 (香港)、法文 (加拿大、法國)、德文、西班牙文 (墨西哥、西班牙、美國)。這意味著將來新 Firmware 更新 Siri 可以支援更多的語言（包括廣東話）。希望 Apple TV 也快點加入支援廣東話吧 !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiYZAAw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiYZAAw.png&h=da683fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/12/06/homepod-hk/shop_guide/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2Fhomepod-hk%2Fshop_guide%2Famp%2F&d=L%2Be77Tmv9%2F%2FNkSuSKe7P5DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=80485431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.hk/2018/12/06/homepod-hk/shop_guide/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"bbe9600612feeeb94ceda86461c6518c50d7a118","tid":931003,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:18:59.000Z","msg":"用緊澳洲版"},{"pid":"1c1613377581a3d45d4edd817c8889453ba0d1a7","tid":931003,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a1ddd05b404136fd30f21876c3f15c10e75354d","tid":931003,"uid":46418,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"1c1613377581a3d45d4edd817c8889453ba0d1a7","tid":931003,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T1